<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>elections</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            height: 100vh; /* Full height of the viewport */
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f0f4f8; /* Light background color */
            color: #333; /* Dark text for contrast */
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem; /* Larger font size for the heading */
            margin-bottom: 20px; /* Space below heading */
            color: #4CAF50; /* Green color for the heading */
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.2rem; /* Slightly larger text */
            text-align: center; /* Center align the text */
            margin-bottom: 30px; /* Space below paragraph */
            padding: 0 20px; /* Add some padding for better readability */
        }

        a {
            display: inline-block; /* Allow padding and margin */
            padding: 15px 30px; /* Add padding to the button */
            background-color: #4CAF50; /* Green background */
            color: white; /* White text color */
            text-decoration: none; /* Remove underline */
            border-radius: 5px; /* Round the corners */
            transition: background-color 0.3s, transform 0.3s; /* Animation for hover effect */
        }

        a:hover {
            background-color: #45a049; /* Darker green on hover */
            transform: scale(1.05); /* Slightly grow the button on hover */
        }

        /* Responsive design */
        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            h1 {
                font-size: 2rem; /* Smaller font size on mobile */
            }

            p {
                font-size: 1rem; /* Smaller text on mobile */
            }

            a {
                padding: 12px 25px; /* Adjust padding for smaller screens */
                font-size: 1rem; /* Font size for mobile */
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>SRKR Engineering College</h1>
    <p>Hi, I am Naveen, a dedicated member of the ACE organization at SRKR Engineering College. I have been actively involved in various initiatives that aim to enhance the student experience and promote collaboration among peers. Now, I am honored to be nominated for the position of President of ACE. I believe my leadership skills and passion for our community will help us achieve great things together. Vote for me, and let's make a difference together. Thank you for your support!</p>
    <a href="/index">Click This to Elect Me!</a>
</body>
</html>
